data.description: Don't miss this stunning, updated home that sits on a large corner lot, within walking distance to the library, local schools, Starbucks, and more! With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a large basement bonus room that could even double as a 5th bedroom, this home has space galore! The meticulous yard is sure to be your new oasis, and did I mention there is RV parking? Best of all, NO HOA! That's right, NO HOA in this gorgeous neighborhood. The new solar panels are only $131.70 a month, and are under warranty. If the buyer assumes the solar loan, they will be eligible for an $8,000.00 tax credit! This spectacular home will go fast, so schedule your showing asap!
